data.meta_description: moam.info_list-of-unclaimed-dividends-stanbicibtcinves_5a1d54841723ddba458a1833 - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document is a list of unclaimed dividends from 2011 by shareholders of Stanbic IBTC Bank PLC. It provides the names of over 500 shareholders who did not claim their dividend warrants. The affected shareholders are instructed to contact the Managing Director of First Registrars in Lagos with proof of ownership to claim their outstanding dividends.
